Xuanfeng?

00:00:59.140 --> 00:01:00.832
(The Legend of Heroes)

00:02:19.844 --> 00:02:20.574
=Duel on Mount Hua=

00:02:20.574 --> 00:02:22.912
(Adapted from Jin Yong's novel,
The Legend of the Condor Heroes)

00:02:23.012 --> 00:02:25.888
=Nine Yin True Sutra=
=Episode 7=

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:58.656
Xuanfeng.

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:02.400
Why would you do that?

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:06.919
I just fell asleep.

00:03:08.120 --> 00:03:09.479
Must be overexerting in training.

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:11.968
Don't lie to me.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:15.479
You took arsenic.

00:03:23.159 --> 00:03:24.159
I...

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:25.152
I'm using it to boost

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:26.719
my internal strength.

00:03:27.199 --> 00:03:28.120
Taking arsenic to boost

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:29.439
internal strength?

00:03:29.919 --> 00:03:31.759
It's all about the Nine Yin True Sutra.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:34.599
So you've been taking arsenic recently?

00:03:35.159 --> 00:03:36.680
Any mistake could cost you your life.

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:41.120
I just want you to know,

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:42.464
for you,

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:43.560
I would do anything.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:50.912
Xuanfeng.

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.879
Thank you for everything.

00:03:57.280 --> 00:03:59.360
I possess nothing of value,

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:01.440
and you can take

00:04:02.039 --> 00:04:03.104
whatever you desire.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:07.280
But I just want

00:04:08.599 --> 00:04:09.479
to revenge.

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:13.319
You misunderstand me.

00:04:13.919 --> 00:04:16.720
This isn't as dangerous as you imagine.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:18.839
With proper application

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:19.920
and precise dosage,

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:20.839
one can rapidly

00:04:20.839 --> 00:04:21.759
boost internal strength

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:23.160
without causing bodily harm.

00:04:25.639 --> 00:04:27.120
Through recent experiments,

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:29.199
I know

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:30.319
the proper arsenic dosage.

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.199
I'll take it with you.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:01.160
Why are you here again?

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:02.560
Don't exert yourself.

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:04.120
Master is in seclusion.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:05.720
What if you trigger premature labor?

00:05:05.959 --> 00:05:06.848
My Lady.

00:05:08.839 --> 00:05:10.839
I must write down
Nine Yin True Sutra once more.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.560
Only it can save Yaoshi.

00:05:26.959 --> 00:05:27.968
My Lady.

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:30.592
My Lady!

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:31.648
My Lady!

00:05:32.439 --> 00:05:33.280
My Lady!

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:39.040
Save the child.

00:07:16.100 --> 00:07:18.528
(Heroes' Haven, Land of Blessings)

00:07:45.988 --> 00:07:51.104
(Heroes' Haven, Land of Blessings)

00:08:01.079 --> 00:08:02.240
Save the mother or the child?

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:04.800
Mother.

00:08:05.879 --> 00:08:06.784
Yes.

00:08:19.519 --> 00:08:20.439
Save the child.

00:08:32.480 --> 00:08:33.840
My time is limited.

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:39.960
Save the child.

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:16.000
Try standing up.

00:10:18.679 --> 00:10:19.680
Slowly.

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:41.376
Try again.

00:11:18.784 --> 00:11:25.728
(Grave of Taohua Island's Lady Feng)

00:11:27.039 --> 00:11:27.919
(You once said,)

00:11:29.840 --> 00:11:31.039
(when a daughter is born,)

00:11:32.039 --> 00:11:33.639
(we'd bury a jar of wine.)

00:11:36.080 --> 00:11:37.399
(When Rong comes of age,)

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:40.559
(we'd drink it together.)

00:11:40.676 --> 00:11:43.232
(Living in Drunken Haze)

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:44.559
(By then,)

00:11:46.120 --> 00:11:48.159
(the past is beyond recall,)

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:52.919
(and future remains unknown.)

00:11:56.159 --> 00:11:58.039
(Feng Heng shall exist no more.)

00:12:00.080 --> 00:12:01.000
(Then why)

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:03.120
(would Huang Yaoshi)

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:07.399
(exist then?)

00:12:07.872 --> 00:12:11.680
♪Traverse thousands of miles of land
with every step♪

00:12:12.064 --> 00:12:15.072
♪Half a lifetime
witnessing the changes of the world♪

00:12:15.904 --> 00:12:22.848
♪Never thought love
could wound me so mercilessly♪

00:12:23.072 --> 00:12:27.360
♪My azure robe withstands
a thousand crashing waves♪

00:12:27.360 --> 00:12:29.952
♪Unaware of suffering so long♪

00:12:31.264 --> 00:12:34.880
♪Yet this passion might shatter♪

00:12:34.880 --> 00:12:38.656
♪Leaving me adrift♪

00:13:12.600 --> 00:13:13.480
It seems

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:14.360
you've recovered.

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:16.360
Nine Yin True Sutra is amazing.

00:13:18.080 --> 00:13:19.136
From now on,

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:21.759
we may start practicing

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:22.960
advanced techniques.

00:13:23.759 --> 00:13:24.799
The martial arts recorded

00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:25.856
are numerous.

00:13:26.039 --> 00:13:27.000
Where shall we begin?

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:28.960
I've studied it.

00:13:30.080 --> 00:13:32.512
Nine Yin Skeleton Claw,
Heart-Breaking Palm,

00:13:33.080 --> 00:13:34.112
and White Serpent Whip.

00:13:34.279 --> 00:13:37.240
These three require
no foundation of mental method.

00:13:37.679 --> 00:13:38.656
We can master them fast.

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:44.519
However, cultivating these techniques

00:13:44.600 --> 00:13:47.000
demands an unorthodox method.

00:13:47.840 --> 00:13:48.759
Unorthodox method?

00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:25.840
I thought you feared nothing.

00:14:26.759 --> 00:14:27.720
Seems I was wrong.

00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:31.360
Why brought me here?

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:34.944
Ghosts!

00:14:39.039 --> 00:14:40.032
Not funny.

00:14:44.720 --> 00:14:46.120
The sutra says,

00:14:47.759 --> 00:14:49.600
those practicing
the Nine Yin Skeleton Claw

00:14:50.799 --> 00:14:52.480
focus all internal strength
on ten fingers,

00:14:52.559 --> 00:14:53.519
to grasp hard objects.

00:14:54.200 --> 00:14:55.392
Human skulls are the optimal.

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:57.720
If one pierces holes on them
without fracturing them,

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:00.159
then one masters

00:15:01.279 --> 00:15:02.336
Nine Yin Skeleton Claw.

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:09.279
I brought you here

00:15:10.039 --> 00:15:11.399
because we need skulls.

00:15:55.908 --> 00:15:58.976
(Living in Drunken Haze)

00:16:15.320 --> 00:16:16.224
Beautiful.

00:17:28.160 --> 00:17:29.039
Who is there?

00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:30.496
Identify yourselves!

00:17:31.920 --> 00:17:33.240
Our identities don't matter.

00:17:33.599 --> 00:17:34.599
You two

00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:36.000
provoked Yunhai Manor.

00:17:36.319 --> 00:17:37.839
Now there's a 100-tael bounty

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:40.319
for your heads.

00:17:41.559 --> 00:17:43.440
So you're Qiu Yunhai's lapdogs.

00:17:44.319 --> 00:17:45.440
A 100-tael bounty?

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.072
Let's see if you

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:48.160
are capable to get it.

00:18:18.119 --> 00:18:19.240
What a sinister technique!

00:18:20.119 --> 00:18:21.720
No wonder you are here for skulls.

00:18:23.480 --> 00:18:24.448
You've been tracking us?

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:26.759
Using skulls for practicing.

00:18:27.279 --> 00:18:28.519
Must be up to nothing good.

00:18:29.119 --> 00:18:29.960
Kill Mei Chaofeng.

00:19:17.839 --> 00:19:18.839
Xuanfeng.

00:19:18.839 --> 00:19:20.039
Why my Nine Yin Skeleton Claw

00:19:20.359 --> 00:19:21.880
works well against torsos and limbs,

00:19:22.559 --> 00:19:23.640
yet my energy flow

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:25.799
gets obstructed

00:19:26.200 --> 00:19:27.136
when striking heads,

00:19:27.319 --> 00:19:28.319
causing me stuck?

00:19:28.768 --> 00:19:29.799
The human skull

00:19:29.799 --> 00:19:31.200
is the hardest armor,

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:33.440
and the hardest part to break through.

00:19:35.519 --> 00:19:36.839
You're still new to it.

00:19:37.079 --> 00:19:38.319
It's normal to find it hard.

00:19:38.599 --> 00:19:40.079
But when I practice with skulls,

00:19:40.559 --> 00:19:41.720
why energy flows smoothly?

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:46.496
Perhaps

00:19:47.279 --> 00:19:48.960
because they are lifeless objects,

00:19:49.400 --> 00:19:50.880
while living foes reinforce with qi.

00:19:51.759 --> 00:19:52.680
Though your control

00:19:52.720 --> 00:19:53.799
remains imperfect,

00:19:54.200 --> 00:19:55.079
your current progress

00:19:55.319 --> 00:19:56.576
is already remarkable.

00:19:58.000 --> 00:19:59.519
I must practice harder

00:20:00.039 --> 00:20:01.039
to achieve breakthrough.

00:20:01.952 --> 00:20:03.000
No.

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:04.032
Haste breeds failure.

00:20:04.519 --> 00:20:05.504
Breakthrough requires

00:20:05.680 --> 00:20:06.920
patience and opportunity.

00:20:08.279 --> 00:20:09.240
Just recuperate for now.

00:20:09.599 --> 00:20:10.519
Don't rush.

00:20:14.079 --> 00:20:14.944
I have an idea.

00:20:15.359 --> 00:20:16.640
I'll take you out to relax.

00:20:25.279 --> 00:20:26.208
Come take a look.

00:20:40.519 --> 00:20:41.408
Do you like it?

00:20:41.720 --> 00:20:42.640
I know nothing of art.

00:20:44.039 --> 00:20:45.640
But I think Lingfeng might like it.

00:20:46.039 --> 00:20:47.119
Let's buy it for him.

00:20:51.400 --> 00:20:52.279
Mister.

00:20:52.279 --> 00:20:53.344
We'll take this painting.

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:54.880
Alright.

00:20:56.400 --> 00:20:58.359
This Go set for Chengfeng.

00:20:58.799 --> 00:20:59.759
This silver scale

00:21:00.119 --> 00:21:01.152
for Mianfeng.

00:21:01.839 --> 00:21:03.359
Mofeng loves mechanisms.

00:21:03.839 --> 00:21:05.559
This turtledove

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:06.592
will suit him well.

00:21:07.480 --> 00:21:09.079
Madam must look good

00:21:09.279 --> 00:21:10.144
with it.

00:21:11.684 --> 00:21:15.520
(Variety Store)

00:21:16.920 --> 00:21:18.016
This longevity locket...

00:21:19.240 --> 00:21:20.720
When we return,

00:21:21.079 --> 00:21:22.400
the child of Master and Madam

00:21:22.640 --> 00:21:23.640
must have been born.

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:25.119
It's a perfect gift.

00:21:27.780 --> 00:21:30.368
(Sun's Tailor Shop)

00:21:53.640 --> 00:21:54.960
To boost internal strength

00:21:56.519 --> 00:21:57.839
with drugs bears hidden costs.

00:21:59.680 --> 00:22:00.640
Will it heal?

00:22:02.680 --> 00:22:03.744
Unless

00:22:03.880 --> 00:22:04.759
we cease practicing.

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:05.880
We can't.

00:22:08.192 --> 00:22:09.160
Even if we

00:22:09.240 --> 00:22:10.519
offer these gifts as an apology,

00:22:12.519 --> 00:22:13.680
will they forgive us?

00:22:16.640 --> 00:22:18.319
We're just deceiving ourselves.

00:22:41.400 --> 00:22:42.759
Don't ladies adore such things?

00:22:43.599 --> 00:22:44.519
Yet you never use them.

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:47.599
I don't know how.

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:49.088
I can help.

00:22:50.400 --> 00:22:51.240
As a child,

00:22:52.079 --> 00:22:53.160
I saw Mother apply makeup

00:22:53.559 --> 00:22:54.480
and picked up basics.

00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:05.039
(So it was him playing the flute)

00:24:05.759 --> 00:24:07.559
(on Taohua Island that lulls me)

00:24:08.200 --> 00:24:09.119
(to sleep.)

00:24:31.519 --> 00:24:32.880
Back on Taohua Island,

00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:36.359
I never knew you could play the flute.

00:24:59.960 --> 00:25:01.039
Xuanfeng.

00:25:01.039 --> 00:25:02.960
Tomorrow we'll seek
revenge against Qiu Yunhai.

00:25:03.680 --> 00:25:04.720
I'll make you dumplings.

00:25:05.680 --> 00:25:06.784
What filling do you like?

00:25:09.000 --> 00:25:09.952
Well...

00:25:10.640 --> 00:25:11.680
I'm fine with anything.

00:25:13.279 --> 00:25:14.839
Then we'll use whatever we have.

00:25:15.400 --> 00:25:16.720
Go get some fresh vinegar.

00:25:51.480 --> 00:25:52.352
Xuanfeng.

00:25:52.640 --> 00:25:53.640
We're also out of ginger.

00:25:53.759 --> 00:25:54.599
Buy some.

00:25:55.079 --> 00:25:55.968
Xuanfeng.

00:25:57.119 --> 00:25:58.272
Xuanfeng?

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:21.792
Cousin.

00:26:21.792 --> 00:26:22.680
(Chen Zhihe of Yingchuan)
Long time no see.

00:26:28.599 --> 00:26:29.559
Are you alone?

00:26:29.559 --> 00:26:30.560
As you see.

00:26:31.480 --> 00:26:32.400
You used a secret code.

00:26:32.839 --> 00:26:33.856
What's the matter?

00:26:34.759 --> 00:26:36.680
Lu Chengfeng sent a letter to the Chens,

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:39.279
saying you stole
Nine Yin True Sutra with Mei Chaofeng

00:26:39.400 --> 00:26:40.680
and betrayed them.

00:26:41.519 --> 00:26:42.560
Is that true?

00:26:43.240 --> 00:26:44.359
I didn't betray them.

00:26:45.480 --> 00:26:46.920
So the theft did happen.

00:26:47.920 --> 00:26:48.896
In that case,

00:26:49.200 --> 00:26:50.200
our elders

00:26:50.200 --> 00:26:51.279
have a message for you.

00:26:52.064 --> 00:26:53.248
(Chen)
Heed the command.

00:26:54.319 --> 00:26:55.920
Kill Mei Chaofeng immediately

00:26:56.319 --> 00:26:58.359
and return with the Nine Yin True Sutra.

00:26:59.440 --> 00:27:00.799
What do they want it for?

00:27:01.319 --> 00:27:02.200
Rumors say

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:04.119
the Nine Yin True Sutra
has supreme techniques.

00:27:04.839 --> 00:27:06.279
Master it and one'll be invincible.

00:27:07.039 --> 00:27:08.480
Our clan isn't a martial arts sect.

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:10.000
Why meddle in it?

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:11.000
The clan wants

00:27:11.000 --> 00:27:12.680
to master various techniques,

00:27:12.680 --> 00:27:13.640
hoping to

00:27:13.640 --> 00:27:15.519
restore our former glory.

00:27:17.079 --> 00:27:18.799
That's why they sent you to Huang Yaoshi

00:27:19.799 --> 00:27:20.800
back then.

00:27:21.000 --> 00:27:22.519
It can't restore the family's glory.

00:27:22.880 --> 00:27:24.480
The elders have their own calculations.

00:27:25.759 --> 00:27:27.039
As the young master,

00:27:27.119 --> 00:27:28.200
you must obey.

00:27:29.119 --> 00:27:30.559
Unless you've forgotten

00:27:30.559 --> 00:27:32.759
our family teachings and the cause.

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:33.888
Or rather,

00:27:34.680 --> 00:27:36.640
you no longer consider yourself a Chen.

00:27:42.359 --> 00:27:43.360
I haven't forgotten.

00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:44.960
Let me think about it.

00:27:45.200 --> 00:27:46.336
Wait for my news.

00:27:49.200 --> 00:27:50.799
I'll come for it tonight.

00:28:02.359 --> 00:28:03.279
(Heed the command.)

00:28:04.000 --> 00:28:05.480
(Kill Mei Chaofeng immediately)

00:28:06.079 --> 00:28:07.920
(and return
with the Nine Yin True Sutra.)

00:28:08.000 --> 00:28:09.119
(Xuanfeng)

00:28:09.519 --> 00:28:10.680
may appear

00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:12.119
unrestrained,

00:28:13.039 --> 00:28:14.000
but deep down,

00:28:14.400 --> 00:28:16.400
(he carries
an unresolved burden from the past.)

00:28:17.119 --> 00:28:18.680
(He's one of the Chens of Yingchuan.)

00:28:19.240 --> 00:28:20.279
(After their decline,)

00:28:20.599 --> 00:28:22.400
(the family hoped he)

00:28:22.559 --> 00:28:23.839
could restore its past glory.

00:28:24.119 --> 00:28:25.119
Xuanfeng believes

00:28:25.119 --> 00:28:26.119
this is but a pipe dream,

00:28:26.160 --> 00:28:27.119
destined to vanish.

00:28:27.599 --> 00:28:28.640
Yet in reality,

00:28:28.799 --> 00:28:30.359
he can't fully let it go.

00:28:31.680 --> 00:28:32.799
(Unless you've forgotten)

00:28:32.799 --> 00:28:33.880
(Chen)
our family teachings

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:35.168
and the cause.

00:28:35.168 --> 00:28:36.279
I haven't forgotten.

00:28:36.279 --> 00:28:37.312
Let me think about it.

00:29:19.599 --> 00:29:20.640
Everything's ready?

00:29:23.880 --> 00:29:24.928
You bought wine?

00:29:28.640 --> 00:29:30.000
And the outfit you liked.

00:29:34.799 --> 00:29:35.808
Let's eat.

00:29:51.000 --> 00:29:51.840
Tomorrow,

00:29:52.039 --> 00:29:53.240
we'll set off to Yunhai Manor.

00:29:54.359 --> 00:29:55.519
We've been waiting so long.

00:29:55.519 --> 00:29:56.384
We deserve a toast.

00:30:30.279 --> 00:30:33.279
The two of us drank cup after cup

00:30:35.720 --> 00:30:38.640
among the blooming mountain flowers.

00:30:39.720 --> 00:30:42.920
I'm already drowsy from drinking,
and you can leave.

00:30:44.759 --> 00:30:48.279
Come back with the qin tomorrow morning.

00:30:52.519 --> 00:30:53.519
After we left the island,

00:30:55.839 --> 00:30:56.680
I thought

00:30:57.839 --> 00:30:58.799
to follow you

00:30:59.799 --> 00:31:00.759
wherever you go

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:04.599
all my life.

00:31:23.480 --> 00:31:24.839
Master once told me

00:31:25.920 --> 00:31:27.119
not to fear forgetting.

00:31:28.359 --> 00:31:30.119
With no one or nothing else

00:31:31.440 --> 00:31:32.416
deserves remembering,

00:31:34.079 --> 00:31:35.160
then you won't forget.

00:31:38.119 --> 00:31:39.039
He was right.

00:31:41.960 --> 00:31:43.008
Chaofeng.

00:31:44.079 --> 00:31:45.120
What do you mean?

00:31:48.640 --> 00:31:49.504
Xuanfeng.

00:31:52.160 --> 00:31:53.519
Thank you for

00:31:54.440 --> 00:31:55.584
being with me.

00:31:56.319 --> 00:31:57.312
